{"tid":1485274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"走啦，唔好諗住留係度捉鬼or幫手","createTime":"2019-08-18T15:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:49:05.000Z","uid":168911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d7183526da6cb73761368c8e588474f922c24c3f","tid":1485274,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:45:49.000Z","msg":"鬼係捉唔哂的，捉到你都做唔到乜野 (你又唔會報警)<br />\n反而你存在就會製造環境比鬼存在<br />\n令你自己身處險境<br />\n<br />\n又或者你諗住要&quot;幫手&quot;，想&quot;做D野&quot;<br />\n但係其實你今晚安全番屋企，就係最大幫手<br />\n來緊呢個星期，就睇住政局既變化，係要時間蘊釀<br />\n你估佢地會一路睇fb live一路諗應對咩? 官方當下只會出&quot;罐頭&quot;回應<br />\n班狗官只會office hour先做野，政局變化係發生得好慢<br />\n我地set好deadline，擇日再戰，就可以keep住momentum<br />\n<br />\n又或者你地有其他理由? 我唔明你地仲留係度做乜<br />\n當我蠢，你答下我?"},{"pid":"264b4c2726cc13d41b678796a6e878ccee0e7c40","tid":1485274,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"015900365e782ef49466575ba7bea255e8f9d4af","tid":1485274,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:59:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"20693b4935ff6708f3b20ff9554a99bf3ca16f34","tid":1485274,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:01:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cfb90f9462bb56bdb3550d2affbfc330deeccc44","tid":1485274,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:06:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a689d25bed84948ea127de0f4e9ab74d0170dc0b","tid":1485274,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:08:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f0b9e3def1cec76b59c6f5b3a4942093fe5a785e","tid":1485274,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:13:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4ad68582bda9cc3c587740d595a3ec80cfa3afac","tid":1485274,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:49:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">感謝前線朋友</span>"}]}